#. Tag: member
#: man-kdesvn.1.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Full user documentation is available through the &khelpcenter;. You can also "
"enter the &URL; <emphasis>help:/kdesvn/</emphasis> directly into &konqueror; "
"or you can run <emphasis>`khelpcenter help:/kdesvn/'</emphasis> from the "
"command-line."
msgstr ""
"De volledige gebruikers documentatie is beschikbaar via het &khelpcenter;. U "
"kunt ook de &URL; <emphasis>help:/kdesvn/</emphasis> direct in &konqueror; "
"invoeren maar u kunt ook <emphasis>`khelpcenter help:/kdesvn/'</emphasis> "
"van de commandoregel uitvoeren."

